"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        RNGParameters structures with different FIPS186 variation fields.
        """
a = objects.RNGParameters(fips186_variation=enums.FIPS186Variation.
    GP_X_ORIGINAL)
b = objects.RNGParameters(fips186_variation=enums.FIPS186Variation.X_ORIGINAL)
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
